  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*: Rotate device to landscape mode -> UI is shown in portrait (as expected). Now shake device to get Instabug popup. It's shown in landscape mode. \r\n![instabug landscape](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6584810/25130965/66a0dc02-2444-11e7-96b7-cff32feeb645.png)\r\n\r\nClose popup -> UI is shown in landscape mode and looks broken (half of the Chats list is empty). If navigate to other screens and rotate device then list is also half-empty.\r\n![ui landscape](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6584810/25130970/6a0c9818-2444-11e7-8d6d-56d3d63123f6.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nUI is shown in portrait mode \r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\nUI is shown in landscape mode. Half of the Chats list is empty\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status and login\r\n- Turn device to landscape mode\r\n- Shake device to get Instabug popup\r\n- Tap on empty place to close popup\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: 0.9.5-57\r\n* Operating System: Android \r\n",
